#

Tzatziki Sauce

10 min
$3.5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Greek

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

SauceDipGreekHealthy

Description

A refreshing Greek yogurt sauce with cucumber and garlic, perfect for dipping or as a salad dressing.

Ingredients

  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • cucumber (grated): 1 medium
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • dill (fresh or dried): 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
